                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390617-1729-offence-1 t18390617-cd-12"></join>23rd of May</rs>, 51 yards of linen cloth, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390617-name-136" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-136" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
